ZH: 这个房间里有一面大镜面。
EN: There is a large mirror in this room.

ZH: 她站在镜面前整理着自己的发型。
EN: She stood in front of the mirror fixing her hair.

ZH: 他看着镜面里的自己，感到有些不满意。
EN: He looked at himself in the mirror and felt a bit dissatisfied.

ZH: 镜面反射出阳光，照得房间一片明亮。
EN: The mirror reflected the sunlight, brightening up the room.

ZH: 孩子们在镜面前比划着自己的动作。
EN: The children gestured their movements in front of the mirror.

ZH: 镜面上面有些污迹，需要清洁一下。
EN: There are some dirt marks on the mirror, it needs to be cleaned.

ZH: 她镜面里的倒影仿佛在微笑。
EN: Her reflection in the mirror seemed to be smiling.

ZH: 请你用镜面看看你的脸，看看有没有什么不舒服的地方。
EN: Please look at your face in the mirror and see if there is anything uncomfortable.

ZH: 他花了很长时间整理镜面上的头发。
EN: He spent a long time fixing his hair in front of the mirror.

ZH: 镜面可以反射出物体的形状和颜色。
EN: The mirror can reflect the shape and color of objects.

ZH: 请小心不要打碎了镜面。
EN: Please be careful not to break the mirror.

ZH: 镜面的边缘刚刚被装饰了一圈金色的边。
EN: The edges of the mirror were just decorated with a golden rim.

ZH: 她通过镜面尝试了一下新的化妆品。
EN: She tried out the new makeup through the mirror.

ZH: 我在镜面前反复练习表演。
EN: I practiced my performance repeatedly in front of the mirror.

ZH: 镜面的反射让我看到了一个全新的自己。
EN: The reflection in the mirror showed me a whole new self.

ZH: 请小心不要碰到镜面，容易破裂。
EN: Please be careful not to touch the mirror, it's easy to break.

ZH: 那块镜面可以放在墙上作为装饰品。
EN: That mirror can be placed on the wall as a decoration.

ZH: 镜面里的倒影似曾相识。
EN: The reflection in the mirror seemed familiar.

ZH: 镜面反射的图片非常清晰。
EN: The images reflected by the mirror are very clear.

ZH: 她在镜面上看到了自己的母亲的影子。
EN: She saw the shadow of her mother in the mirror.
